<doc f='include/theora/codec.h' l='568'>/**Look up the number of instances of a tag.
 * Call this first when querying for a specific tag and then iterate over the
 *  number of instances with separate calls to th_comment_query() to
 *  retrieve all the values for that tag in order.
 * \param _tc    An initialized #th_comment structure.
 * \param _tag   The tag to look up.
 * \return The number on instances of this particular tag.*/</doc>
